This product builds on and incorporates ideas and components from:

Goose
  https://github.com/block/goose
  Copyright Block, Inc.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

  rockie-nugget uses Goose as its MCP-native agent runtime base. Goose
  provides the model-agnostic loop, MCP extension host, and headless
  execution that rockie-nugget configures with the research-env-v1 tool
  contract.

Model Context Protocol (MCP)
  https://modelcontextprotocol.io
  The tool contract in contract/ and the server in mcp/research-env-mcp/
  implement the open Model Context Protocol.

SUPER (Allen Institute for AI)
  https://github.com/allenai/super
  Copyright The Allen Institute for Artificial Intelligence.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

  eval/adapters/super/grade.py vendors SUPER's deterministic evaluate()
  scoring function verbatim, used to grade agent output for the SUPER
  benchmark adapter.
